Package: SWATbuildR
Type: Package
Title: An object connectivity based SWAT+ model builder.
Version: 1.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Christoph", "Schuerz",
                email = "c.schuerz@posteo.org",
                role = c("aut", "cre"),
                comment = c(ORCID = '0000-0002-7204-5828'))
Maintainer: Christoph Schuerz <c.schuerz@posteo.org>
Description: `SWATbuildR` makes use of the new SWAT+ hydrological objects
  to set up SWAT+ models with fully connected land and water objects. Unlike
  model setups built e.g. with QSWAT+, fractions of water and nutrient fluxes
  are routed between contiguous land objects and water objects instead of 
  lumping HRUs in routing units. This new routing approach should facilitate
  a better representation of water and nutrient transport in the landscape.
